34
00:01:13,360 --> 00:01:17,120
if you take their cultural tour package in
Taiwan.

35
00:01:19,420 --> 00:01:23,430
I had my suspicions about this “cultural
trip.”

36
00:01:23,430 --> 00:01:25,240
As a wise man once said,

37
00:01:25,240 --> 00:01:27,149
fool me once shame on you.

38
00:01:27,149 --> 00:01:28,429
Fool me twice,

39
00:01:28,429 --> 00:01:31,279
um, can’t get fooled again?

40
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:34,900
But the rich beauty of Taiwan called to me.

41
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:47,920
You’re right,

42
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:50,060
