52
00:02:28,860 --> 00:02:32,459
There were jars filled with Chinese herbs.

53
00:02:32,459 --> 00:02:34,709
And tea.

54
00:02:34,709 --> 00:02:36,069
The perfect place to relax

55
00:02:36,069 --> 00:02:39,819
