81
00:04:10,760 --> 00:04:14,160
Oh yeah, this was going to be fun.

82
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:17,400
Focus.

83
00:04:17,400 --> 00:04:18,400
Dedication.

84
00:04:18,400 --> 00:04:19,600
Scissors.

85
00:04:20,760 --> 00:04:22,670
I’m not a man making shoes,

86
00:04:22,670 --> 00:04:25,440
I’m a shoe-making man.

87
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:47,600
One piece down.

88
00:04:52,940 --> 00:04:53,760
Hard.

89
00:04:53,760 --> 00:04:56,040
Apparently really hard.

90
00:05:01,440 --> 00:05:02,480
Hi, Shelley!

91
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:03,680
Hi, Chris.

92
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:06,490
How did the women’s shoemaking class go?

93
00:05:06,490 --> 00:05:08,090
It went great.

94
00:05:08,090 --> 00:05:11,120
I made these for you!

95
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:12,200
Really?

96
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:15,380
Wow, they’re actually really nice.

97
00:05:15,380 --> 00:05:17,770
Thanks Chris, that’s really sweet.

98
00:05:17,770 --> 00:05:19,720
No problem, um,

99
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:21,350
