108
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:41,280
I wonder what Aiyu jelly is.

109
00:05:41,280 --> 00:05:42,860
And coffin bread…

110
00:05:42,860 --> 00:05:44,640
So you can cook?

111
00:05:44,640 --> 00:05:46,240
How hard can it be?

112
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:44,000
Chris!

113
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:46,140
Chris, we need to go on that

114
00:06:46,140 --> 00:06:47,480
