115
00:06:54,400 --> 00:06:57,320
A tour of Tainan in southern Taiwan!

116
00:06:57,360 --> 00:07:00,640
Our first stop was the famous Confucian Temple.

117
00:07:02,320 --> 00:07:05,170
No con-fusion about it.

118
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:09,040
That was the best Confucian Temple I’d ever
been to.

119
